Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:39.45,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,487)\fad(1000,1000)}Um raio de luz {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:41.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está Reiju? {SC815 3:20:02}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não faço ideia.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela saiu há um tempo.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:46.71,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(520,0)}QUARTO DE HÓSPEDES DA FAMÍLIA VINSMOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:48.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:49.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:50.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:51.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá preto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:52.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chá verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Qual você deseja?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.42,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Qual você deseja?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:02:00.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas, pai, onde Sanji \Ne sua esposa vão morar depois de se casarem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É óbvio que será em Germa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:10.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não a tomarmos como refém, \Nquem sabe que condições eles nos imporão.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles são piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como refém, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:22.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com certeza eles também querem manter Sanji como refém por precaução, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não diga bobagens, Niji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:31.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que fosse assim, você acha que \Nnos afetaria se matassem Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem dito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou morrendo de ansiedade...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:42.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...para viver junto com Sanji novamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:48.39,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(670,545)\fad(540,0)}MIRRO WORLD - CASA DE BRÛLÉE {SC814 11:07:21}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero ser comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estão com fome, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos morrendo de fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.63,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Estamos morrendo de fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:21.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esta será a presa mais saborosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Croac, croac!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.64,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Não me comam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me soltem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:29.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desista.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.78,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Brûlée cavou sua própria cova.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.83,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:04.29,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Aquela Carrot que foi capturada \Ncomigo era uma impostora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:10.85,Pensante,,0,0,0,,É um sapo que foi transformado no\N reflexo de Carrot pela habilidade de Brûlée.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.31,Pensante,,0,0,0,,A verdadeira Carrot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.74,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...está no sótão.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me comam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:29.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Croac, croac!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:27.60,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.45,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Chormano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:32.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:39.46,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mas eu ficaria com pena se cozinhassem o sapo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.66,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Há dezesseis inimigos nesta casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:49.62,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Os mais problemáticos\N são Randolph, Nobledilo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:53.00,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Diesel, o misterioso homem chaminé,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.70,Pensante,,0,0,0,,e Brûlée.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.61,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Minha única chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.68,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...é o momento em que \Ndeixarem a Carrot falsa cair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Randolph, corte a corda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando cair, ela vai se mover muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Teremos que tampar rapidamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vamos nós, Brûlée-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.34,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Agora, Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Postura de lançamento...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Randolph?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:52.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée-sama, apareceu alguém no telhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há duas coelhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:05.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se mexa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rápido, Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo, Chormano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que ela vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Randolph!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Corte a corda agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:48.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:51.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Q-Queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Queima, queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Croac.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.88,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Q-Queima!{\an8} {SC815 6:39:66}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.17,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eletrical Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.32,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2630,3130)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.32,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2630,3130)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.32,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2630,3130)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.32,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2630,3130)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.32,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2630,3130)}Lua Elétrica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preciso avisar a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu cuido disso, Chormano!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:42.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ninguém pode me alcançar\N quando eu começo a correr...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:42.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Garchú!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem sou eu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, não, não...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ainda não!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tá bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,V-Vou bater!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não consigo parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Derrotamos Brûlée e seus capangas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chormano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:24.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora podemos usar a habilidade de\N Brûlée para entrar e sair dos espelhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:29.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos usar este mundo para\N procurar todos na ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:33.71,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(527,281)}QUARTO DE SANJI {SC815 4:46:51}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Posso entrar-nasu?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:34.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por trazer tudo isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De nada-nasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, tenho algo para te dizer-nasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:47.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Capturamos Luffy do Chapéu de Palha\N e a Gata Ladra-nasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:52.14,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Luffy e Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:09.00,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,474)}Se você não fugir, tudo\N será resolvido pacificamente, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:15.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, agora mesmo um mink e\N o Soul King estão causando estragos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.88,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:22.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Smoothie-sama, a general doce, e\N Barão Tamago foram subjugá-los,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:24.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mas está sendo muito difícil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já chega.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:26.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E os ingredientes que eu pedi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, aqui estão-nasu.
Comment: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:36.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nota: Este homem termina suas frases com Nasu: Berinjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:38.07,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2630,3130)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.68,0:10:38.07,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2630,3130)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.68,0:10:38.07,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2630,3130)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:10:32.68,0:10:38.07,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2630,3130)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:32.68,0:10:38.07,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2630,3130)}Nota: Este homem termina suas frases com Nasu: Berinjela {nota presente apenas no pace, achei uma boa adição}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:36.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se estiver com fome, posso\N trazer uma berinjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou usar esta cozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:41.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:49.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding-chan não foi jantar, \Nentão vou preparar algo para ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendo-nasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou preocupado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:11:00.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, ouvi dizer que ela não está se sentindo bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.72,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,412)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(670,545)\fad(250,250)}Quarto\N do tesouro {one pace only infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,São estas, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pedro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou te decepcionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja! {SC815 11:48:64}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como você se atreve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro que sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Swallow Banderole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.52,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2740,3240)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.52,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2740,3240)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.52,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2740,3240)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.52,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2740,3240)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.52,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2740,3240)}Bandeirola de Andorinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:52.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu pedi ao meu companheiro que arriscasse\N a vida antes de eu vir aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se eu não alcançar meu objetivo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não poderei olhar em seus olhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:20.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Embora eu não tenha olhos para olhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Guardas, vocês estão me ouvindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Respondam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preciso me apressar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:50.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O intruso está dentro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:54.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não precisava vir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu cuido disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saia da frente, Smoothie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é você,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:18.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,o insolente que se atreve...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:22.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...a arruinar minha diversão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que é...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:40.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que criatura estranha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:52.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O intruso está passando\N pelo corredor perto do jardim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rodeiem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Escudos à frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ao ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quase lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós o encurralamos no jardim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que vocês querem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo sem nos vermos-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:46.19,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(490,0)}JARDIM DO WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Barão Tamago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:53.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pedro, capitão dos Piratas Nox!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:58.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Embora você seja meu inimigo,\N tem todo o meu respeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Toda vez que te vejo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:06.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,a cicatriz no meu olho esquerdo\N dói-toi et moi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há cinco anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:15.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...você foi a extremos\N para se agarrar à vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:19.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você voltou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não tem muito tempo\N de vida-soufflé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:28.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Naquele dia, mama tirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:39.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...cinquenta anos da sua vida-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, estou ciente.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu não planejo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...voltar vivo para casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:37.01,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(533,0)}SWEET CITY {SC816 1:05:45}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, um fantasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqui também não está.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estará ainda mais longe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acorde, Brûlée!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde estão os espelhos do Whole Cake Château?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Diesel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não sabe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro que não!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:32.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Enquanto tocarmos em Brûlée, \Npodemos entrar e sair dos espelhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:38.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este lugar está conectado a todos\N os espelhos da Ilha Whole Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não devemos demorar para ver o castelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acorde!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Caramba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:49.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, teremos que\N procurar sozinhos até ela acordar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos correr até encontrar um!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:58.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão pagar por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:11.55,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(134,415)\fad(250,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}BIBLIOTECA \NPRISÃO {one pace only infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:09.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está pensando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É inútil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:21.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você não parar, vai perder as mãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso que estou tentando fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:24.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nada disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:33.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há outra forma de sair daqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:37.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É melhor perder os braços do que morrer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mais um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles estão ficando mais finos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim está bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Enquanto esperamos alguém\N vir nos salvar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:19:01.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,vamos perder tudo e Big Mom\N vai nos matar no final!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bobagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:07.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero morrer assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Arranque seus braços também!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está louco?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:16.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:20.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, eu cuido disso, \Nentão não se meta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero ver você perder os braços!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:23.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não seja tão egoísta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:31.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...não vou morrer aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:47.01,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(184,430)\fs23}QUARTO DE \NHÓSPEDES DE SANJI, \NWHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU {pace only infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:47.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preparei como de costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:51.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não acho que Pudding-chan coma tanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que estou pensando?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:20:00.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, se sobrar, eu como.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.43,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Tanto assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.47,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mas não consigo comer tanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.50,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Coma você também, Sanji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.20,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Abra a boca.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.27,Sanji in Love,,0,0,0,,Tomara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding-chan, espere por mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vai sair-nasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:33.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, vou animar meu único\N raio de luz neste mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, quer esta berinjela?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depois.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.48,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(512,0)}WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU - JARDIM DO TERCEIRO ANDAR
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:04.45,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,485)\fad(538,0)}PEDRO, EX-CAPITÃO DOS PIRATAS NOX
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:04.45,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,715)\fad(538,0)}RECOMPENSA 382 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:13.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,475)\fad(525,0)}BARÃO TAMAGO, CAVALEIRO DOS PIRATAS DE BIG MOM
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:13.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,715)\fad(525,0)}RECOMPENSA 429 MILHÕES DE BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:21.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha e a Gata Ladra\N já caíram em nossas mãos-bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desista-bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E daí?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:29.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, vamos acertar as contas-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:01.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não tenho medo de mink-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você se preparou, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:04.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou usando meias especiais\N para me proteger do electro-feuille.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:11.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou acertar as contas com você\N de uma vez por todas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:14.81,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,São meus irmãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:15.92,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você é...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:16.84,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:18.24,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Irmão Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:19.27,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Irmão Zepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.50,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Garchú!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:22.25,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Garchú...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:23.67,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Garchú!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:24.61,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Garchú...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:26.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:31.31,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Gao, sou um membro dos\N Piratas de Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:37.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,702)}Desta vez não será só um olho!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:37.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,702)}Desta vez não será\N só um olho!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:11.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:19.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ainda há momentos em que\N meu olho esquerdo dói-feuille.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:23.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu me lembro da dor\N quando você me feriu-toilette!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também não esqueci.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.84,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vocês conseguiram, ladrões.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:39.68,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.14,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:23:57.41,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou tirar cem anos da sua vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:03.29,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Zepo, aguente!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:09.78,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Zepo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.78,0:24:11.80,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Zepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:16.51,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Irmão Zepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:20.95,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ele não conseguiu completar os cem anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.00,0:24:27.09,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Só restavam trinta anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.36,0:24:34.70,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Como você é seu companheiro,\N você deve pagar o resto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:43.46,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1397)}Vamos, me dê os setenta anos restantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:45.18,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Por favor, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:47.27,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ele era como um irmão para mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.27,0:24:51.42,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Se você tirar setenta anos, meu\N irmão Pedro também morrerá!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.42,0:24:52.96,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Chega, Pekoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.96,0:24:54.45,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É patético-bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:24:56.57,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu te imploro, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.57,0:24:57.64,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Pekoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.34,0:25:02.72,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não chore, Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.72,0:25:04.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.60,0:25:06.56,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Dez anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.56,0:25:08.77,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou tirar apenas dez anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.77,0:25:10.31,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Mas o quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.44,0:25:16.48,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Mas o crime de tirar o olho\N de Tamago é grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.45,0:25:19.20,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou tirar sessenta anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.90,0:25:30.00,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Alguma objeção, Pekoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.00,0:25:32.73,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,B-Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.51,0:25:40.18,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ei, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.91,0:25:45.31,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Quantos anos você vai me tirar agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.22,0:25:49.90,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1038)}Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.71,0:25:53.98,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não faz sentido morrer aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.98,0:25:56.70,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O amanhecer do mundo está próximo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.70,0:25:58.87,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu preciso voltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.60,0:26:09.22,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Que homem bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.22,0:26:12.30,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou reduzir para cinquenta anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.30,0:26:15.24,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,892)}Viva.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.76,0:26:21.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Leg Benedict!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.76,0:26:21.20,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:26:18.76,0:26:21.20,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:26:18.76,0:26:21.20,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:26:18.76,0:26:21.20,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:26:18.76,0:26:21.20,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Perna beneditina.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.41,0:26:29.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Responda-bon, Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.50,0:26:32.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você voltou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:41.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para esta ilha de pesadelo onde seu\N companheiro morreu e você perdeu cinquenta anos de vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.72,0:26:48.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,518)}Os Chapéus de Palha\N salvaram nosso país!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.81,0:27:04.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, acredito que são eles\N que levarão o mundo ao amanhecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.20,0:27:13.15,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.15,0:27:18.11,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O amanhecer do mundo está chegando!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.73,0:27:30.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha vão\N superá-los e mudar o mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.42,0:27:34.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que eles podem fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.16,0:27:36.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde você acha que está-bon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.84,0:27:39.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a Ilha Whole Cake-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.26,0:27:41.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E daí?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.69,0:27:45.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu acredito nos Chapéus de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.06,0:27:49.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso vou dar o pouco que\N me resta de vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.58,0:27:53.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...sem remorsos!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.69,0:28:01.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas não me entenda mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.20,0:28:03.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou morrer aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.74,0:28:07.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles ainda não alcançaram\N seu objetivo nesta ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.03,0:28:27.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou morrer ainda.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.85,0:28:31.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que há de errado?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.14,0:28:32.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você me deixou passar há um tempo.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.86,0:28:34.81,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(410,496)}FRENTE AO QUARTO DE PUDDING
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.77,0:28:35.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é não, bobinho.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.20,0:28:36.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.23,0:28:42.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding-sama está ocupada!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.24,0:28:43.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ocupada?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.86,0:28:46.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está fechado, bobinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.08,0:28:48.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vá embora, bobinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.40,0:29:06.09,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Espere um momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.09,0:29:10.40,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O quarto de Pudding-chan\N tinha uma varanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.62,0:29:31.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou entregar pela janela.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.87,0:29:37.50,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Será inapropriado?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.50,0:29:39.61,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Vão pensar que estou espionando.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:43.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, mas amanhã seremos marido e mulher.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.95,0:29:46.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que ela esteja se trocando...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.34,0:29:50.72,Sanji in Love,,0,0,0,,M-Mesmo que esteja nua,\N não será um crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.43,0:30:00.06,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Que bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.06,0:30:01.92,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ela tem energia para rir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.78,0:30:05.40,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Aí está ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:07.58,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Pudding-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.45,0:30:10.83,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Com quem ela está falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.79,0:30:14.25,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Reiju?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.25,0:30:16.30,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O que ela está fazendo aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.30,0:30:18.49,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O que ela está fazendo com Pudding-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.31,0:30:31.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare de sonhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.26,0:30:34.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que eu vou me casar com aquele patife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.35,0:30:36.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro que não!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.80,0:30:40.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}Claro que não!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.18,0:30:49.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sou a queridinha da mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.10,0:30:50.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por minhas habilidades de atuação.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.99,0:30:55.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ultimamente ela me mimou tanto\N que estou começando a ficar cansada.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.16,0:31:01.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É fácil enganar um homem\N por ordens da mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.17,0:31:04.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O caso dos Chapéus de Palha\N também foi moleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.89,0:31:11.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só minha família conhece\N minha verdadeira personalidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.93,0:31:21.06,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(401,0)}BIBLIOTECA PRISÃO
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.06,0:31:23.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.98,0:31:27.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossa, cala a boca-fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.61,0:31:31.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga de Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.66,0:31:33.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy, pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.24,0:31:35.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você vai mesmo perdê-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.78,0:31:38.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.29,0:31:46.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,986)}...a perdoarei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.82,0:31:50.59,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Então fiquem tranquilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.47,0:31:54.76,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não vou me casar com ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.37,0:31:59.52,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Escutem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.48,0:32:05.54,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não vou me casar...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.25,0:32:10.61,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...com aquele idiota que se\N apaixonou completamente por mim...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.53,0:32:16.78,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...porque durante a cerimônia...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.24,0:32:21.12,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...eu mesma vou matá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.08,0:32:28.46,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, vocês\N também não sairão vivos.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:42.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera, Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.60,0:32:44.55,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.77,0:32:50.28,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Adeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.28,0:32:52.34,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ratos patéticos.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.61,0:32:58.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desde o início ela armou uma armadilha para nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.49,0:33:01.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que ela tem contra o Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.03,0:33:02.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que saco!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.87,0:33:07.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que ingênuos vocês são!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.16,0:33:12.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso de Germa 66, o exército do mal?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.16,0:33:16.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Continuem acreditando em suas fantasias, idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.38,0:33:27.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O objetivo da mama sempre\N foi conseguir o exército de clones...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.30,0:33:30.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e sua tecnologia!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.61,0:33:42.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas que personalidade você tem...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.92,0:33:45.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, você é desafiadora.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.66,0:33:51.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não temos nada a tratar com vocês, que são desobedientes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.69,0:33:56.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todo o Reino de Germa está\N ancorado em nosso território.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.82,0:34:01.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,São como moscas presas em algo doce,\N neste caso, o casamento político de Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:03.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.53,0:34:06.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo foi de acordo com o plano da mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.39,0:34:11.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No casamento de amanhã,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.68,0:34:16.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,todos os Vinsmoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.81,0:34:22.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...serão aniquilados!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.50,0:34:50.86,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTempos:\NUmim,\NHalee\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e acene...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para que futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos há muito tempo.
